Order flow: CUSTOMER → ORDER_TABLE → ORDER_ITEM (junction table, many-to-many between orders and products) → SHIPMENT → COURIER.
Audit & tracking: DELIVERY_EVENT captures every status update for a shipment (proof photo URL, exception type, notes), and STATUS_HISTORY is the audit log table — it tracks any entity's status change over time with old/new values and who made the change. This is the detail that pushes the schema into the 9–10 band.

